tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,
review: I am incredibly grateful for the exceptional care I received from Dr. Teena during my pregnancy and delivery. From our first appointment, Dr. Teena made me feel comfortable and well-informed. She always took the time to answer my questions and provided thorough explanations for all the procedures, which was very reassuring.I highly recommend her for her exceptional professionalism and support. She knows what is the best, you can fully trust her and follow her advice to get the best. She guided us on everything including diet, exercises, mental health, weight management.We were able to deliver the baby girl through normal delivery without epidural and I recovered completely within 2 weeks.All thanks to her and the team.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
Dr.Teena is very good doctor. If anyone having issues in getting pregnancy , I suggest to take treatment from Dr.Teena .  I was planning for pregnancy from past 2 years but I wasn't and  after taking treatment from Teena , within 4 months I got conceived.
It's apparent that Dr.Teena really care about patients. The way she handles patient is very much impressive. She prefers C-Section surgery when it is really required only. I never found commerc nature in her. I was in impression that I can't go for normal delivery as I am very lean and not having that much strength so got very scared about normal delivery and requested for C-section , Even though I asked for C-section delivery she didn't go for it and I got normal delivery and blessed with baby girl.
Nowadays doctors don't have time to give proper treatment to patients because of their busy schedules but Dr.Teena will give sufficient time to each patient.
*** ** *** ** *** **** ****** * **** **** I can't thank you enough for the excellent care she has provided.  Thank you so much for the great treatment.

review: I highly recommend Dr Teena ,She explains the things clearly and guide well the patient. She make feel ease like family member and always approachable. She is very good and provide moral support to patient for normal support. Personally Thank you Very much Mam.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,
review:
If you really want to visit a good and genuine Doctor who is true to her profession from the depth of her heart Dr Teena is the one.I am very thankful to god that we met. And with God's grace and the ample support of Teena mam, i delivered my baby boy (normal delivery) on 27 sep '21 under her guidance with her cheerful  and energetic voice to give me extra energy to push as I was getting tired towards the end!
I would like to highlight some of the key thing which i found splendid in her which makes me decide to continue my pregnency journey with her :-
1:-She always support natural delivery and advised some exercise which I must tell helps a lot in my delivery.
2:- The best thing is she spends a good amount of time with patients and explain everything in detail & gives a road map.
3:-She is very friendly, calm,grounded and completely patient centric.
4:-I had the history of 1 miscarriage but after that she never went us to go through genetic test as She made us understand that these will be unnecessary for our age and advised us to wait for 2 months and then go ahead.
5:-She never prescribe any unnecessary medicine and scans or test.
6:-Knowing my prior history (1st miscarriage), she took intensive precautions and monitored me and my baby very closely during the first trimester .
7:-she's always available and responsive on whatsapp for doubts and queries . I always kept Dr Teena informed about anything which I felt was odd. Her responsiveness helped me keep myself calm/positive and also avoided unnecessary trips to the clinic for every small question.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,
review:
My wife Promin Singha was pregnant and we were very worried due to two miscarriages previously. Since my wife was very weak, we were in dilemma whether to continue the pregnancy.
Upon advise by our colleague, we visited Dr.Teena mam and explained her about our situation. Firstly, she was very patient to listen our history and the problems we had. She thoroughly reviewed all previous investigations and informed the possible reasons for the miscarriages. 
Madam was very positive and convinced us to continue the pregnancy. However, we were still worried of further unknown complications. Madam really took a special care of my wife, regularly monitored, advised her with a healthy diet plan with simple exercise and asked my wife to strictly follow for better health of both. She was in regular touch with us throughout the pregnancy and we could reach her anytime. This really helped us to stay positive and my wife was very much attached to madam. Finally, with all the support and guidance, my wife normally delivered baby boy, we are so blessed to see healthy baby.
Her patience, positive approach, guidance and the trust we had that madam will be there during any complications kept us positive. We are very happy and feel a complete family now.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
context: Normal Vaginal Delivery (NVD),Pre and Post Delivery Care,
review: Wonderful experience with Dr. Teena Mam.She is very friendly,helpful and kind. She ensured I had a smooth prep, delivery , and follow-up. She suggested me prenatal classes for normal delivery. My experience during labour and delivery was also very great. The behaviour of doctor at that movement matters a lot and Dr Teena Mam handle it very peacefully and maintain courage required at that movement.I am so glad I chose Dr Teena Mam and would highly recommend to anyone. One more great thing is she answers query on what’s app too . I am very much thankful to god that I  met her. Thank you very much Mam for everything.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,
context: Pregnancy Check Up,Pre and Post Delivery Care,
review:
The way a Mother take care of her child ...same way Teena mam takes care of her patient.  We consulted Teena madam for our Pregnancy planning , and then she turned our pregnancy journey to a beautiful story . The way she took care every part of this story is amazing. A doctor with so kind hearted and friendly make you feel really great. She gives time to problems , listen them carefully and approachable any time and never hesitated to answer over call or msg. Mam always try to guide you in best possible practical and cost effective way. She is like an angle to us ... by holding her hand and with god's blessings our baby came to our lap. We still miss her like an family member and definitely recommend Teena Mam!!!

Thank you so much Teena Mam for all support and  greatest happiness you have given us.

We have consulted Dr.Teena madam for my wife's pregnancy in the Vaatsalya clinic. Right from the beginning till the 9th month of her pregnancy and for the delivery process we got fabulous support from Teena mam and were finally blessed with a baby boy at Rainbow hospital, Marathahalli.

Madam is very energetic, positive attitude with friendly nature, explains things in detail, and gives support in every matter. Lucky to come in contact with mam and get her support throughout our exciting journey of us.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,
review: My wife was very depressed due to irregular cycles and miscarriage. We met Dr.Teena upon our friends advise. Firstly, she patiently listened to our concerns, reviewed all our previous reports and explained to us in a best possible way we understand. She explained us for the prescribed examination and treatment, why it is required and how it will help us to go forward. The best part is, Dr.Teena can be reached anytime and get clarified for any queries. Our treatment is ongoing, and we see positive results in her treatment. We highly recommend her.

tags: Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,Doctor friendliness,
review:
Dr. Teena is one of the most patient, compassionate and empathetic "Obstetrics and Gynaecologist" I have met till now.

She gives time to explain the situation from her perspective and prepares the patient to deal with it. I have had days when our consultation session would end in just 5 mins and then there were days when she gave complete half an hour or so to check, explain and listen to what I had to say.

Once my BP was showing high which is usually normal so she engaged me in general friendly conversations. Once I was at ease she checked it once again & the BP turned out to be normal. I felt so good and well attended.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,
review:
I consulted Dr.  Teena as part of general health check up at Narayana hirudalay Whitefield.  I have been having yearly health checkups every year since past 8 years so I have seen how casually doctors examine you as part of health checkup...  

But opposite to my usual experience,  she did examine me very throughly and seriously. This made me think that if she can examine a patient who's checkup  is complementary one then how she will treat her own patients..

So the day I got pregnant,  I went to her without doubt.. She does her practice very ethically,  n does not make your pregnancy part of today's corporate health industry.  

When I went to my home town n started consulting other gynaecologists, I actually realized how comfortable she made my pregnancy whereas other doctor were scaring me for compliacations n c-sections. I reached out to her again,  followed her advice n had a comfortable  normal delivery and a 3.5 kg healthy baby girl.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,

Dr Teena is very caring about there patient health and her primary goal to have as normal delivery.

Thank you Dr Teena for all your support and guidance

Finally, my mother was convinced and agreed and she underwent hysteroscopy for polyp removal. We are very thankful to Dr.Teena for her patience and guidance. We highly recommend her.
